graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:AdminCreateCountryInput!)
{
	adminCreateCountry (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		iso3166Alpha2
		iso3166Alpha3
		iso3166Numeric
		customCode
		prefix
		image
		sort
		administrativeAreas
		latitude
		longitude
		zoom
		dataLang
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	adminGetCountries (query: $query)
	{
		id
		iso3166Alpha2
		iso3166Alpha3
		iso3166Numeric
		customCode
		prefix
		image
		sort
		administrativeAreas
		latitude
		longitude
		zoom
		dataLang
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
